{"author":{"id":"4bb6c1767e50694cfde61856db22bf137d1651e8a0b5ca858c486db3dd02f280"},"ops":[{"type":3,"timestamp":1778696207,"nonce":"1I2TDYIwCjiCHxPUU1ThNQgzDmw=","message":"**Vel-RMSE values corrected after go-cue alignment fix (`06f7faf`).**\n\nThe headline within-cell vel-RMSE values in `results/3702f54/notes/analysis.md` were originally computed by averaging trial-mean profiles in absolute trial time before the pairwise-RMSE step. `centerout`'s target-on duration is randomised per trial, so this smeared the go cue across ~150 ms and biased the RMSE values. The fix re-locks each trial to its own go cue before the trial-axis collapse.\n\nHold drift, pre-go RMS, peak vel, and TTP are scalar per-trial metrics that already used per-trial go-cue indexing and are unchanged.\n\n| Cell | Pre-fix vel-RMSE | Post-fix vel-RMSE | Δ |\n|---|---:|---:|---:|\n| lit__post_nojerk | 0.0361 | 0.0383 | +6% |\n| lit__full_nojerk | 0.0414 | 0.0428 | +3% |\n| post_go_pl__pos10 | 0.1394 | 0.1824 | +31% |\n| full_trial_pl__pos10 | 0.1047 | 0.1426 | +36% |\n| full_trial_pl__prego_1e-3 | 0.0221 | 0.0299 | +35% |\n| full_trial_pl__prego_5e-2 | 0.0244 | 0.0311 | +27% |\n| **full_trial_pl__prego_1** | **0.0176** | **0.0255** | **+45%** |\n| full_trial_pl__pos10_prego_1e-3 | 0.1272 | 0.1780 | +40% |\n| full_trial_pl__pos10_prego_5e-2 | 0.0520 | 0.1109 | +113% |\n| full_trial_pl__pos10_prego_1 | 0.1511 | 0.1841 | +22% |\n\n**Verdict unchanged.** `full_trial_pl__prego_1` still wins decisively. Vel-RMSE shifted up across the board, but the ordering, the matrix-winner margin, and the discard verdict on `__pos10` are all preserved.\n\nFixed by commits `53362d9` / `0e14755` / `c7a7883` / `35769d1` on `feature/go-cue-alignment-fix`.","files":null}]}